en_192168_0	The investigations into the murder of Ranjan de Silva, father of cricketer Dananjaya de Silva, have been handed over to the Criminal Investigations Department.
en_192168_1	Police Media Spokesperson said that several other police teams have also been appointed to assist the investigations.
en_192168_2	The Police Special Task Force arrested 3 suspects in connection to the incident in Angulana recently.
